386
00:23:43,830 --> 00:23:44,810
It's all right.

387
00:23:44,890 --> 00:23:45,990
Who told you they're not usable?

388
00:23:51,630 --> 00:23:52,730
Liang Mu Ze!

389
00:23:53,390 --> 00:23:54,590
