because it has fleas!

394
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:01,790
Aunt, don't worry.

395
00:24:01,870 --> 00:24:03,270
I've de-wormed it.

396
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,190
That's useless. It's still dirty.

397
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,390
You can't raise it.

398
00:24:06,470 --> 00:24:07,490
Come, give it to me.

399
00:24:08,020 --> 00:24:09,010
Meaty!

400
00:24:12,230 --> 00:24:13,270
I'll tell you what.

401
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:15,150
I have found an adopter.

402
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:16,710
It's one of my friends in Ningjiang.

403
00:24:16,790 --> 00:24:18,790
-They have many cats in their house.
-What a relief!

404
00:24:18,870 --> 00:24:20,300
You guys are busy working every day.

405
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:22,500
How can you guys take care of it?

406
00:24:22,580 --> 00:24:25,450
It's good for either side to send it away,
