407
00:24:27,090 --> 00:24:28,230
You know nothing!

408
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:29,650
You're really stubborn!

409
00:24:35,850 --> 00:24:36,780
What is this?

410
00:24:37,230 --> 00:24:38,290
What are you pulling out?

411
00:24:48,300 --> 00:24:49,260
It's a tapping device.

412
00:24:50,930 --> 00:24:52,010
You didn't...

413
00:24:52,750 --> 00:24:54,010
install this, right?

414
00:24:54,090 --> 00:24:55,280
Of course not.

415
00:25:01,620 --> 00:25:03,760
I handed the tapping device
to the technical department.

416
00:25:03,840 --> 00:25:05,270
They said it's a professional device.

417
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:07,930
Yes, the installation technique
was professional too.

418
00:25:08,430 --> 00:25:11,570
We searched everywhere that day.

419
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:13,410
But we didn't expect...

420
00:25:13,490 --> 00:25:15,830
