in the cat's collar.

421
00:25:17,930 --> 00:25:18,820
Thank you.

422
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:25,070
-Did you leak any confidential info?
-No.

423
00:25:25,150 --> 00:25:26,660
This is the basic military capacity.

424
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:29,700
After leaving the military camp,
my chat context is only about my life.

425
00:25:29,780 --> 00:25:32,800
Moreover, I've taken preventive measures
that day...

426
