after I suspected someone broke
into my house.

427
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:36,440
Good.

428
00:25:36,980 --> 00:25:38,060
Did you check the camera footage
of the district?

429
00:25:38,140 --> 00:25:39,100
I checked it on the day.

430
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:40,200
Nothing was found.

431
00:25:41,150 --> 00:25:42,970
Who do you think it might be?

432
00:25:46,990 --> 00:25:47,860
Zhuo Ran.

433
00:25:51,550 --> 00:25:53,240
He asked someone to switch...

434
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:55,160
the sleeping pills
which Xia Chu gave to me.

435
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:56,700
But based on what he said,

436
00:25:57,430 --> 00:25:58,770
he didn't know the pills were for me.

437
00:25:59,850 --> 00:26:03,230
He did it out of his concern for Xia Chu.

438
00:26:04,350 --> 00:26:06,410
I certainly never believed
in his explanation.

439
00:26:07,950 --> 00:26:09,600
But I don't understand.

440
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:13,300
Because Xia Chu improvised
the pills for me the night before.

441
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:15,950
The pills happened to be switched
the next morning.

442
00:26:16,820 --> 00:26:18,930
And I found this tapping device today.

443
00:26:19,010 --> 00:26:20,210
All I could think is him.

444
00:26:21,100 --> 00:26:23,600
Do you guys have any history
before the pills were switched?

445
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:26,370
I wouldn't call it that.

446
00:26:27,390 --> 00:26:30,190
Just that, he was Xia Chu's first love.

447
00:26:30,990 --> 00:26:33,430
Xia Chu is currently staying in my house.

448
00:26:33,510 --> 00:26:36,930
So you think he did that for Xia Chu.

449
00:26:37,010 --> 00:26:38,750
I found no other reason.

450
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:51,460
Mr Zhuo?

451
00:26:53,870 --> 00:26:54,750
You're here.

452
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,950
Did you ask someone to keep an eye on him
after the medical forum?

453
00:27:00,450 --> 00:27:01,330
I did.

454
00:27:02,390 --> 00:27:05,030
But this guy has high vigilance.

455
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:07,060
