between Ningjiang and Dong'an.

458
00:27:14,690 --> 00:27:17,150
But we didn't know where he went,
and who he met.

459
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:20,910
He went to Dong'an?

460
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:25,510
Mr Zhuo, is the matter of a paymaster...

461
00:27:25,590 --> 00:27:27,520
that's going to start
a pharmaceutical company in Dong'an...

462
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,750
that you'd mentioned before reliable?

463
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:29,990
Of course.

464
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:33,050
Professor Xia already agreed
to be our technical consultant.

465
00:27:33,590 --> 00:27:34,730
Teacher agreed?

466
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:37,180
It's currently in a confidential phase.

467
00:27:37,260 --> 00:27:40,930
When the conditions are right,
his inauguration will be announced.

468
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,630
No wonder.

469
00:27:43,710 --> 00:27:44,720
No wonder what?

470
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:46,980
He sent an email to me
via his personal mailbox.

471
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:52,030
Asking me to send him the data of a kind
of sedative in the current clinical trial.

472
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:53,790
I thought there was something wrong.

473
00:27:53,870 --> 00:27:55,780
I thought his email was hacked.

474
00:27:55,860 --> 00:27:57,620
You are the apprentice
whom he's most proud of.

475
00:27:57,700 --> 00:28:00,800
He certainly wishes to take you with him
if he leaves the institute.

476
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:01,790
Then...

477
00:28:01,870 --> 00:28:04,020
Then he should tell me in advance.

478
00:28:04,100 --> 00:28:06,870
