and asked the security to talk to me.

479
00:28:06,950 --> 00:28:08,650
What was all that about?

480
00:28:08,730 --> 00:28:10,470
Professor Xia has his own difficulty.

481
00:28:11,350 --> 00:28:14,800
The point is there are many
inexplicable things in the current phase.

482
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:17,980
There will be many gossips,
especially in your institute.

483
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:19,880
We should follow the procedure.

484
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:23,660
You're right.

485
00:28:23,740 --> 00:28:26,670
But I didn't expect Teacher
would leave too.

486
00:28:27,580 --> 00:28:30,000
Who wouldn't leave if there's a way?

487
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:35,670
Dr Tang, I'm not going to deceive you.

488
00:28:37,040 --> 00:28:39,670
This is a factory building contract
in two copies.

489
00:28:40,120 --> 00:28:41,190
Take a look.

490
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:42,950
