is 100,000 dollars per month?

494
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:56,150
This is the fee
for the preliminary preparation.

495
00:28:57,070 --> 00:28:59,670
We'll pay you immediately
after you sign the contract.

496
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:00,930
This is for your first month.

497
00:29:03,450 --> 00:29:04,760
After the factory is built,

498
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:08,040
