according to your personal performance.

499
00:29:08,120 --> 00:29:10,130
The greater the contribution,
the higher the wages.

500
00:29:14,780 --> 00:29:16,780
Did Teacher already sign this?

501
00:29:16,860 --> 00:29:17,790
He did.

502
00:29:18,670 --> 00:29:22,370
After all,
your institute is only a platform.

503
00:29:22,840 --> 00:29:26,340
It's obvious that we can give you
more than the vanity title...

504
00:29:26,420 --> 00:29:27,610
it gives you.

505
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:41,070
I kept reviewing
the background of this guy,

506
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:44,050
but nothing wrong was found.

507
00:29:45,520 --> 00:29:47,340
What about the 3D-printed gun?

508
00:29:48,070 --> 00:29:52,550
Currently, there's no proof
that he downloaded and printed it.

509
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:56,210
Moreover, he happened to have an alibi...

510
00:29:56,290 --> 00:29:58,190
on the night Gui died.

511
00:29:58,750 --> 00:30:00,960
Any clue at Yunshan Tunnel?

512
00:30:01,430 --> 00:30:03,480
Perhaps we were too late.

513
00:30:03,560 --> 00:30:05,060
