521
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:31,840
Zhuo Ran?

522
00:30:32,450 --> 00:30:34,800
He saved Xue at Yunshan Tunnel?

523
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,760
Yes.

524
00:30:36,760 --> 00:30:37,640
