527
00:30:47,770 --> 00:30:49,460
That's strange.

528
00:30:49,540 --> 00:30:51,440
If he was one of the transaction parties,

529
00:30:51,980 --> 00:30:53,278
his behaviour was tantamount...

530
00:30:53,362 --> 00:30:56,080
