532
00:31:00,950 --> 00:31:01,860
Isn't he afraid?

533
00:31:01,940 --> 00:31:03,960
Some people are born to be a gamester.

534
00:31:06,250 --> 00:31:07,130
Right.

535
00:31:08,470 --> 00:31:11,580
Erasing any trace
after killing someone...

536
00:31:12,080 --> 00:31:13,460
is a kind of disguise.

537
00:31:14,060 --> 00:31:17,390
It might be an advanced method
to hide oneself...

538
00:31:17,470 --> 00:31:20,290
by fully exposing oneself to light.

539
00:31:23,430 --> 00:31:24,860
Just keep an eye on him.

540
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:26,190
I'm sure there's another move coming.

541
00:31:26,710 --> 00:31:28,440
And given everything we know,

542
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:31,958
Xue and Xia Chu can't stay
