00:31:41,130 --> 00:31:43,390
A tapping device
was installed in the house...

547
00:31:43,470 --> 00:31:45,600
of a military officer
of Special Forces Brigade.

548
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:47,340
It's a big deal.

549
00:31:47,890 --> 00:31:49,430
We have to find out the identity...

550
00:31:49,510 --> 00:31:51,890
of the infiltrator and his purpose
as soon as possible...

551
00:31:52,560 --> 00:31:54,130
to avoid further losses.

552
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:57,100
I already informed your unit.

553
00:31:57,180 --> 00:31:58,580
Brigade Commander Dong
will be here tomorrow.

554
00:31:58,660 --> 00:32:02,580
Let's have a brief meeting,
and go through all the information.

555
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:05,620
Okay.

556
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:21,460
Those pills were for me.

557
00:32:21,540 --> 00:32:22,960
He didn't know that.

558
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:26,340
Then how did he know you had these pills?

559
00:32:49,950 --> 00:32:50,970
Miss Lan.

560
00:32:51,050 --> 00:32:55,590
Girl, are you having relationship
with Liang Mu Ze?

561
00:32:55,670 --> 00:32:56,680
No.

562
00:32:57,210 --> 00:32:59,740
Then why did Aunt Mu Min
call to congratulate me...

563
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:01,680
and address me as her in-law?

564
00:33:04,190 --> 00:33:06,110
His mother asked him to go
on blind dates, but he didn't want to.

565
00:33:06,190 --> 00:33:08,530
So he asked me to pretend
to be his girlfriend.

566
00:33:09,350 --> 00:33:10,990
When did this happen?

567
00:33:11,070 --> 00:33:12,520
You actually agreed?

568
00:33:13,230 --> 00:33:14,690
I don't want to move.

569
00:33:15,450 --> 00:33:16,710
Then do you like him?

570
00:33:17,950 --> 00:33:19,050
Be honest with me.

571
00:33:22,860 --> 00:33:23,750
No...

572
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:24,780
You don't like him?

573
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:27,920
I don't know.

574
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:30,570
What do you mean by that?

575
00:33:31,820 --> 00:33:33,080
I just don't know.

576
00:33:34,340 --> 00:33:35,680
Miss Lan, how about you?

577
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:38,530
How did you and my father fall in love?

578
00:33:39,070 --> 00:33:40,610
How did you know...

579
00:33:41,710 --> 00:33:43,130
he's the one?

580
00:33:44,590 --> 00:33:46,310
Girl, I'm hanging up.

581
00:33:46,390 --> 00:33:47,960
I'll call you back
as I've got something to do.

582
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:49,190
What is the matter?

583
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:58,980
Xia, you're back.

584
00:34:02,670 --> 00:34:03,889
Come on in.

585
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:11,719
What's wrong?

586
00:34:39,489 --> 00:34:43,110
Actually, what I'm most worried
is not about losing my reputation,

587
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:48,409
but dragging Tang into this
due to my negligence.

588
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:50,920
He is a talented youth.

589
00:34:51,330 --> 00:34:53,190
If he can't continue participating
in the project,

590
00:34:53,790 --> 00:34:56,130
it's not only his future
that would get affected.

591
00:34:56,210 --> 00:34:57,798
It'd be a great loss for the project...

592
00:34:57,882 --> 00:35:01,660
and the institute's
long-term development too.

593
00:35:10,990 --> 00:35:12,050
It won't happen.

594
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:14,810
You already clarified the causality...

595
00:35:16,240 --> 00:35:17,520
of the matter.

596
00:35:18,150 --> 00:35:22,660
It was omission,
not criminal, like you said.

597
00:35:23,160 --> 00:35:25,420
The institute will find out...

598
00:35:26,060 --> 00:35:28,070
which part that went wrong.

599
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:30,330
Just consider it as taking a break.

600
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:45,761
Actually, for the past two days,

601
00:35:45,845 --> 00:35:49,110
I've been thinking what I can do
if I can't do research anymore.

602
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:53,410
I can't do anything else.

603
00:35:54,710 --> 00:35:56,650
I can't even steam an egg custard.

604
00:35:58,850 --> 00:36:00,800
Do you think it's easy
to steam an egg custard?

605
00:36:01,380 --> 00:36:05,700
Even the most able housewife
can't guarantee...

606
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:09,840
that every egg custard she steams
have no air bubbles.

607
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:12,250
Moreover,

608
00:36:12,990 --> 00:36:15,040
you're not a housewife.

609
00:36:15,120 --> 00:36:16,700
You are Professor Xia.

610
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:18,840
A difference in profession
makes one feel worlds apart.

611
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:26,710
If such a day came,

612
00:36:28,350 --> 00:36:29,970
would you hold it against me?

613
00:36:33,470 --> 00:36:35,170
I've always held it against you,

614
00:36:36,690 --> 00:36:38,750
from the first day I met you.

615
00:36:43,990 --> 00:36:45,290
Do you remember...

616
00:36:46,660 --> 00:36:47,950
you got admitted to our hospital...

617
00:36:48,690 --> 00:36:51,020
when you first suffered from tuberculosis?

618
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:55,030
You had high fever,

619
00:36:55,110 --> 00:36:56,750
haematemesis and cough.

620
00:36:56,830 --> 00:36:58,870
We performed bronchoscopy for you.

621
00:36:58,950 --> 00:37:00,881
You even refused to use anaesthesia...

622
00:37:00,965 --> 00:37:03,515
because you were afraid
it'll affect your intelligence.

623
00:37:11,610 --> 00:37:15,010
The patient we dislike most
is those like you...

624
00:37:15,510 --> 00:37:16,830
who do not cooperate.

625
00:37:19,030 --> 00:37:22,820
Why did you marry me and have child
with me if you dislike me?

626
00:37:24,630 --> 00:37:25,800
That was because...

627
00:37:27,180 --> 00:37:30,450
I found a farewell letter
under your pillow.

628
00:37:33,580 --> 00:37:37,230
You said you were willing
to donate your body...

629
00:37:37,310 --> 00:37:41,520
for medical research purposes
if you couldn't be cured.

630
00:37:43,430 --> 00:37:44,570
And you said,

631
00:37:45,190 --> 00:37:48,500
you're particularly grateful
to a nurse named Lan Zi Yu.

632
00:37:48,580 --> 00:37:51,970
She couldn't find your blood vessel
every time she put you on a drip,

633
00:37:52,050 --> 00:37:54,180
causing her to be on the verge
of breaking down.

634
00:37:54,260 --> 00:37:56,570
You thanked her for giving you...

635
00:37:57,340 --> 00:37:58,760
nice memories...

636
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:03,320
and for cheering you up
at your final moments.

637
00:38:12,750 --> 00:38:16,420
Xia, is there anything harder than this?

638
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:40,150
I dislike every flaw your father has,

639
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:42,670
but I want to love every virtue he has.

640
00:38:42,750 --> 00:38:43,920
Are you like that too?

641
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:05,210
Did you go to the police station?

642
00:39:09,730 --> 00:39:10,990
Why are you still up?

643
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:12,010
I can't sleep.

644
00:39:17,140 --> 00:39:18,810
Xue sent aunt to the airport.

645
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:20,980
I know.

646
00:39:23,020 --> 00:39:24,110
I have something for you.

647
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:25,210
Hold on.

648
00:39:33,700 --> 00:39:35,710
This is the present
that your mother gave to me when she left.

649
00:39:35,790 --> 00:39:36,850
I'll give it back to you.

650
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:40,360
She gave it to you.

651
00:39:41,160 --> 00:39:42,130
Why did you give it to me?

652
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:43,780
I can't have it.

653
00:39:44,220 --> 00:39:45,100
Why?

654
00:39:45,740 --> 00:39:47,130
We're only putting on a show for her.

655
00:39:47,600 --> 00:39:49,950
It's too much if I take it.

656
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:52,210
What do you mean?

657
00:39:54,980 --> 00:39:58,090
She wanted me to ask my parents
to have a meeting with her.

658
00:39:59,070 --> 00:40:00,760
And she asked me to persuade you
to have a career change.

659
00:40:05,830 --> 00:40:07,210
Then how did you reply her?

660
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:11,090
I can only tell her we have no plans
to marry at this point.

661
00:40:12,050 --> 00:40:14,641
We can have a fake relationship,
but we can't have fake marriage.

662
00:40:14,725 --> 00:40:16,835
Marriage will get both sets
of parents involved.

663
00:40:17,630 --> 00:40:19,020
You can blame me
for not keeping my words,

664
00:40:19,100 --> 00:40:20,600
you can ask me to move out too.

665
00:40:20,680 --> 00:40:23,370
Anyway, I can't do this anymore.
I don't want to lie to your mother.

666
00:40:24,930 --> 00:40:25,950
I mean,

667
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:28,050
how are you going to persuade me?

668
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:31,430
What?

669
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:33,470
About changing my career.

670
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:34,840
I'd like you to tell me about it.

671
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:38,270
I have nothing to say.

672
00:40:38,830 --> 00:40:41,630
It's your choice to leave or stay.

673
00:40:45,780 --> 00:40:47,590
Who do you think put the tapping device...

674
00:40:49,350 --> 00:40:50,610
in Er Miao's collar?

675
00:40:51,750 --> 00:40:52,960
I don't know.

676
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:54,280
Try to think.

677
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,580
Can you think of nothing?

678
00:40:59,370 --> 00:41:00,250
Nothing.

679
00:41:01,530 --> 00:41:02,900
Did you ever bring Zhuo Ran back here?

680
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:05,020
What do you mean?

681
00:41:05,100 --> 00:41:06,220
Just what I said.

682
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:07,500
Of course not!

683
00:41:07,580 --> 00:41:08,590
I have no object of suspicion!

684
00:41:08,670 --> 00:41:10,190
Nothing jogs my memory,
and I didn't bring anyone back home!

685
00:41:10,270 --> 00:41:11,490
No one!

686
00:41:11,570 --> 00:41:12,450
I just...

687
00:41:15,690 --> 00:41:16,980
Liang Mu Ze, I don't understand.

688
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,780
Why do you always take aim at Zhuo Ran?

689
00:41:20,790 --> 00:41:21,770
To me,

690
00:41:23,140 --> 00:41:24,970
he's a guy that I knew
when I was 18 years old.

691
00:41:26,070 --> 00:41:28,080
His clean appearance in a white shirt...

692
00:41:28,670 --> 00:41:29,920
was my youth.

693
00:41:31,190 --> 00:41:32,070
How could he...?

694
00:41:34,990 --> 00:41:36,560
How could I suspect him?

695
00:41:38,730 --> 00:41:41,880
So you don't like men in green uniforms,
you like men in white shirts.

696
00:41:41,960 --> 00:41:43,620
Will you listen properly?

697
00:41:43,700 --> 00:41:44,960
Listen to my point, okay?

698
00:41:45,430 --> 00:41:46,390
Calm down.

699
00:41:46,470 --> 00:41:47,540
It's useless to be agitated.

700
00:41:51,890 --> 00:41:52,820
Where are you going?

701
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:55,230
-Let go!
-I don't want to.

702
00:41:55,310 --> 00:41:56,590
Let go of me!

703
00:41:56,670 --> 00:41:57,610
I can't.

704
00:42:36,060 --> 00:42:36,960
What?

705
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:40,180
Liang Mu Ze, we're even.

706
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:45,910
Do you think I'm medical waste?

707
00:42:45,990 --> 00:42:47,070
You ditched me after using me.

708
00:42:49,430 --> 00:42:50,410
I'm tired.

709
00:42:50,940 --> 00:42:52,130
I want to rest.

710
00:43:12,140 --> 00:43:13,830
You said Zhuo Ran
are the memories of your youth.

711
00:43:13,910 --> 00:43:15,540
I have no objection about this matter.

712
00:43:15,620 --> 00:43:19,410
But, Xia Chu, you need to know
the memories of youth...

713
00:43:20,610 --> 00:43:22,150
are not completely reliable.

714
00:43:24,150 --> 00:43:26,920
Have Zhuo Ran told you why he appeared
at the tunnel yesterday?

715
00:43:28,080 --> 00:43:30,480
He said he passed by
while having night run.

716
00:43:32,860 --> 00:43:33,880
Xia Chu,

717
00:43:36,120 --> 00:43:37,810
the dangers in this world...

718
00:43:38,310 --> 00:43:41,280
are much more than you think.

719
00:43:43,090 --> 00:43:45,270
Guarding against strangers
is actually as important...

720
00:43:45,350 --> 00:43:47,130
as guarding against familiar strangers.

721
00:43:47,790 --> 00:43:51,070
So you should train yourself
when you're free.

722
00:43:51,150 --> 00:43:54,670
Do not travel alone
and do not stay in a hotel alone.

723
00:43:55,120 --> 00:43:58,230
Set your speed dial number on your phone
to call the police.

724
00:43:58,310 --> 00:43:59,680
You can call the police
if anything happens.

725
00:44:00,790 --> 00:44:01,820
Wherever you go,

726
00:44:01,900 --> 00:44:05,490
you must remember the location
of the lifts and stairs.

727
00:44:06,010 --> 00:44:06,890
And...

728
00:44:07,380 --> 00:44:09,190
no matter how fast the lift is,

729
00:44:09,270 --> 00:44:12,080
a person running can catch up to it
within three floors.

730
00:44:12,160 --> 00:44:14,110
So if there's any contingency,

731
00:44:14,190 --> 00:44:15,550
you must press the button
for more than three floors...

732
00:44:15,630 --> 00:44:17,170
if you have to take the lift.

733
00:44:17,250 --> 00:44:19,570
You can press multiple floors
to deceive the opponent...

734
00:44:19,650 --> 00:44:20,550
if it's necessary.

735
00:44:21,020 --> 00:44:23,060
If you really couldn't get away,

736
00:44:23,140 --> 00:44:25,950
just keep yourself
surrounded by the crowd,

737
00:44:26,030 --> 00:44:27,130
and yell for help.

738
00:44:27,620 --> 00:44:30,930
Anything around you
can be used as a makeshift weapon.

739
00:44:32,320 --> 00:44:34,480
Anyway, Dr Xia,

740
00:44:34,900 --> 00:44:36,670
you need to learn to protect yourself.

741
00:44:37,180 --> 00:44:38,960
You'll have the chance
to save more people...

742
00:44:39,040 --> 00:44:41,170
only if you can protect yourself.

743
00:44:41,590 --> 00:44:42,490
Do you get it?

744
00:44:45,200 --> 00:44:47,180
Why did you suddenly tell me these?

745
00:44:49,220 --> 00:44:50,530
I'm going to be redeployed.

746
00:44:54,990 --> 00:44:56,330
When do you leave?

747
00:44:56,410 --> 00:44:57,510
It's not certain.

748
00:45:00,590 --> 00:45:02,010
So do you really have nothing...

749
00:45:04,250 --> 00:45:05,910
to tell me about my career change?

750
00:45:09,840 --> 00:45:11,740
Goodnight, Liang Mu Ze.

751
00:45:14,060 --> 00:45:14,940
Goodnight.
